Languages: Python3

Dependent modules:
    Server:
        Load balance: HaProxy-> https://github.com/haproxy/haproxy
        Intranet through: Frp-> https://github.com/fatedier/frp
        
      
        
在 adb shell 中使用 Python 文档已经同步到 blog：
https://kr1s77.github.io/2021/7/12/How-do-I-run-python-on-Android-devices/
    
